Definition: a subtle difference in meaning or opinion or attitude
Example: without understanding the finer nuances you can't enjoy the humor; don't argue about shades of meaning
Synonyms: nicety, shade, subtlety, refinement, verb, change, refine, meaning, a, subtle, difference, in, or, opinion, attitude, without, understanding, the, finer, nuances, you, can, t, enjoy, humor, don, argue, about, shades, of
Category: noun.communication
